Package com.cafean.client.analysis

Interface IntegralElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentElement, ModelElement
    public interface IntegralElement
extends ComponentElement
    An interface describing a ComponentElement that is an integral part of a AbstractComponent. Changes to some or all of an IntegralElement's properties will require an undoable edit for the element's component as well.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      boolean isIntegralProperty​(java.lang.String propertyName)
      Returns true if the given property is to be considered an integral part of this element's component, thus requiring an undoable event for the component.
